---
const items = [
  {
    label: "Cost-saving Solutions",
    detail: "As oil and lubricant wholesalers, you can buy from us by the bulk to save big.",
  },
  {
    label: "Industry Expertise",
    detail: "Over 150 years' combined experience in lubricant formulation, manufacturing, and recycling.",
  },
  {
    label: "High-Quality Products",
    detail: "We offer over 5000 unique products across automotive, industrial, agricultural, and manufacturing sectors.",
  },
  {
    label: "In-House Research & Development",
    detail: "Expert product testing, analysis, and customisable formulations using in-house laboratories. Ensuring tailored solutions for evolving lubrication demands.",
  },
  {
    label: "Friendly, Experienced Team",
    detail: "Our team of local industry experts are here to help guide you in choosing the right oil for your needs, offering bespoke lubricant solutions.",
  },
  {
    label: "Speedy, Nationwide Delivery",
    detail: "We can ship and bulk supply oils, often the next day, across the whole of the UK.",
  },
];
---

<section class="why">
  <div class="why__inner">
    <header class="why__header">
      <h2 class="why__heading">
        Agricultural Lubricant Suppliers West Midlands: Why Choose Midland Oil Group?
      </h2>
      <p class="why__intro">
        With a fully integrated approach to the lubricant lifecycle, from formulation and manufacturing to waste oil collection and regeneration, we offer an all-in-one solution, making us the nation's go-to lubricant suppliers. Choose Midland Oil Group and you'll be choosing:
      </p>
    </header>

    <div class="why__checklist">
      {items.map((item) => (
        <div class="why__item">
          <span class="why__icon" aria-hidden="true">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
              <path d="M4 10.5L8 14.5L16 6" stroke="#c8a034" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
            </svg>
          </span>
          <div class="why__text">
            <strong class="why__label">{item.label}</strong>
            <span class="why__detail">: {item.detail}</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      ))}
    </div>

    <p class="why__distributor">
      We work closely with a large group of distributors, resellers even manufacturers where they require our own labelling/toll blending service. With our in house graphic design, printing facility we can offer multiple batch runs or the client specific one offs in their own branded goods. We stock a large variety of packaging to suit the clients demands, along with varies label offerings this customisable service is a growing part of our organisation and one we are always looking to support our clients alongside.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .why {
    background: var(--page-bg);
    padding: var(--section-py) var(--section-px);
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border-subtle);
  }

  .why__inner {
    max-width: var(--page-max);
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .why__header {
    max-width: 820px;
    margin-bottom: 48px;
  }

  .why__heading {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: clamp(22px, 3vw, 36px);
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.02em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--text-primary);
    margin: 0 0 20px;
    line-height: 1.15;
  }

  .why__intro {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: clamp(15px, 1.5vw, 17px);
    line-height: 1.75;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    margin: 0;
  }

  .why__checklist {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    gap: 24px 48px;
    margin-bottom: 48px;
  }

  .why__item {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 14px;
  }

  .why__icon {
    flex-shrink: 0;
    width: 20px;
    height: 20px;
    margin-top: 2px;
  }

  .why__icon svg {
    display: block;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
  }

  .why__text {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 15px;
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
  }

  .why__label {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: 15px;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
    color: var(--text-primary);
  }

  .why__detail {
    /* inherits font-body from parent */
  }

  .why__distributor {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: clamp(14px, 1.4vw, 16px);
    line-height: 1.8;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    max-width: 860px;
    margin: 0;
    padding-top: 32px;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border-subtle);
  }

  @media (max-width: 700px) {
    .why__checklist {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 20px;
    }
  }
</style>
